## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Generate Prisma client
npm run generate

# Run database migrations
npm run migrate:dev

# Start development server
npm run dev
```

The server starts on [http://localhost:{{ server_port }}](http://localhost:{{ server_port }}).

## API Endpoints

| Method | Path                  | Description        |
| ------ | --------------------- | ------------------ |
| GET    | `/api/v1`             | Welcome message    |
| GET    | `/api/v1/info`        | Service info       |
| GET    | `/api/v1/health/live` | Liveness probe     |
| GET    | `/api/v1/health/ready`| Readiness probe    |
| GET    | `/api/v1/{{ entity_plural }}`       | List items         |
| POST   | `/api/v1/{{ entity_plural }}`       | Create item        |
| GET    | `/api/v1/{{ entity_plural }}/:id`   | Get item           |
| PATCH  | `/api/v1/{{ entity_plural }}/:id`   | Update item        |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/{{ entity_plural }}/:id`   | Delete item        |

## Scripts

| Script         | Description                  |
| -------------- | ---------------------------- |
| `npm run dev`  | Start with hot-reload (tsx)  |
| `npm run build`| Compile TypeScript           |
| `npm start`    | Run compiled output          |
| `npm test`     | Run tests (vitest)           |
| `npm run lint` | Lint with Biome              |

## Docker

```bash
docker compose up -d
```

Starts the app, PostgreSQL, and optionally pgAdmin (`--profile tools`).
